The '''Nizon resistance''' were an organization of [[Nazren]] rebels formed after the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] to oppose the occupation of [[Nizon]] by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], and the exploitation of their species by [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshan]] slavers. The resistance was led by a charismatic individual who only needed an impetus, provided in the form of the [[Alderaanian Resistance]], to [[Battle of Nizon|rise up]] and liberate Nizon.

